INSERT INTO `Posting` VALUES (1,1,'winter','2021-04-17','2021-08-17',1,2000.00,'female',5,5,1,5,0,1,'common','5 bedrooms 2 bathrooms\n\nFull unit at 253 hazel street (not a basement unit, 2nd floor)\n\nLaundry on site\n\n1 parking space provided free\n\nAll utilities and expenses included\n\nFantastic location\n\n2 fridges','2021-04-16 21:51:41','2021-04-16 21:51:41'),(2,2,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-01','2022-09-01',15,820.00,'co-ed',5,5,1,5,0,0,'same-floor','Welcome to myREZ on Lester (181 Lester Street) ! We are located in the centre of the University of Waterloo and WilfridLaurier University. Within walking distance of all the shops, convenience stores, markets, restaurants, and so much more! 5 bed units with In unit laundry, option on walk-in closet, 24/7 video surveillance. On top of that our 18th floor amenities which include gym, business centre, games room, lounge and market! Contact ( Ekam Singh - Leasing) for any leasing inquiries or to book a tour!\n\nTel: 519- 884-8819\n\nE-mail: esingh@offcampusrez.com\n\nVirtual Tour: https://youriguide.com/ohezk_181_lester_st_waterloo_on/','2021-05-14 12:42:05','2021-05-14 12:42:05'),(3,3,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',14,550.00,'female',1,3,1,2,1,1,'common','Looking to sublet my luxurious room for summer 2021\n\n- 1/5 Big room available for sublet from May 2021 - August 2021.\n\n- 2 big bathrooms in the apartment.\n\n- Spacious room and kitchen available.\n\n- Gym in the building, paid parking available.\n\n- Big kitchen with all appliances, refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, oven\n\n- Fully furnished rooms\n\n- Place includes a free WiFi, brand new TV, and sofa set and dining table set.\n\n- Extremely friendly, clean and quiet flatmates.\n\n- All girls apartment.\n\n- Super close to University of Waterloo, short walk to WLU.\n\n- Limited time offer!! Message now!!','2021-04-27 22:43:14','2021-04-27 22:43:14'),(4,4,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-01','2022-09-01',0,715.00,'co-ed',5,5,1,5,0,0,'same-floor','5 Bedroom Suites Available for September 1st. All large bedrooms are fully furnished with private ensuite bathrooms. In-suite Laundry included. Suites have full size Kitchens w/grantie counters, t.v., air conditioning and balconies. Free Ultra High Speed Fibre Internet. Amenities include Fitness Gym, Rec Room, Social Lounge, Study Room and Bike Storage. Heat, water, internet, building maintenance, and amenities included. Hydro extra.\n\nSteps way from Wilfrid Laurier University, University of Waterloo in Conestoga College. Walking distance to Sobeys grocery store, Walmart, restaurants, coffee shops, stores and entertainment.\n\nAsk about the promotions for September 1st.','2021-07-01 20:19:53','2021-07-01 20:19:53'),(5,5,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',14,399.00,'co-ed',1,2,1,3,1,1,'common','Looking for a spring sublet (May - August)\n\n- 1/5 rooms available\n\n- PRICE NEGOTIABLE\n\n- all utilities included (hydro, heating, electricity) + wifi\n\n- largest bedroom fully furnished (chair, bed, drawer, desk)\n\n- 2.5 bathrooms\n\n- dining room\n\n- kitchen (2 fridges)\n\n- on site washing machine and dryer available\n\n- free parking available\n\n- right across from plaza\n\n- 1-5 min walking distance from UW','2021-04-15 20:08:55','2021-04-15 20:08:55'),(6,6,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-01','2022-09-01',18,1758.00,'co-ed',1,3,0,1,0,0,'ensuite','1+1 Bed. 1 Bath\n\nNew building being opened in 2021\n\nHighest floor - 15th Floor\n\n- All inclusive except HYDRO\n\n- Pet friendly\n\n- Very close to UW AND WLU (5 MIN WALK TO BOTH)\n\n- Right in the middle of Waterloo\n\n-Price Negotiable, DM for more info !!','2021-05-14 14:53:29','2021-05-14 14:53:29'),(7,7,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',17,550.00,'male',1,3,1,2,1,1,'same-floor','Looking to sublet my luxurious room for summer 2021\n\n- 1/5 Big room available for sublet from May 2021 - August 2021.\n\n- 2 big bathrooms in the apartment.\n\n- Spacious room and kitchen available.\n\n- Gym in the building, paid parking available.\n\n- Big kitchen with all appliances, refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, oven\n\n- Fully furnished rooms\n\n- Place includes a free WiFi, brand new TV, and sofa set and dining table set.\n\n- Extremely friendly, clean and quiet flatmates.\n\n- All boys apartment.\n\n- Super close to University of Waterloo, short walk to WLU.\n\n- Limited time offer!! Message now!!','2021-04-27 20:15:34','2021-04-27 20:15:34'),(8,8,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-03','2022-09-03',1,750.00,'co-ed',1,2,1,1,0,0,'common','Available: September 2021 to August 2022\n\nYou must sign an N9 form in order for your lease to be only for 12 months, else you will continue your lease for another year\n\nOccupied with 3 Males, 1 Female\n\nLocation: 339 King St N, Waterloo, ON N2J 2Z1\n\nIncludes the Following...\n\n- Fully furnished apartment\n\n- All utilities included: Heating, Water, Electricity, and Internet\n\n- Unlimited wireless internet\n\n- Kitchen includes a large fridge, microwave, and a dishwasher\n\n- Living room includes a TV and couches\n\n- Balcony\n\nSchool is...\n\n- 500 metres walk from WLU (7 minutes)\n\n- 800 metres walk to Conestoga College (8 minutes)\n\n- 3.4 kilometres to UW (42 minutes walk or 13 minutes bus); short bus ride to Waterloo University\n\n- Close to all amenities\n\n- Laundry is $2 per load and an additional $2 for using the dryer\n\n- Individual room lock\n\n- Rent priced below market value\n\n- Students only\n\n- Building facilities include a gym, games room, study room, AND MUCH MORE!\n\nNote: Room numbers are labelled in the pictures. Room B is available now.\n\nIf you would like to see a 3D tour of the apartment, be sure to check out https://kingstreettowers.ca/gallery/ all bedrooms are formatted the same way.','2021-06-24 14:10:59','2021-06-24 14:10:59'),(9,9,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',3,420.00,'female',1,1,0,2,0,1,'unavailable','Fully Furnished | Shared Kitchen | Shared Bathroom with 1 person | Parking Extra | Laundry Included | A/C Included | On Bus Route | Self Contained | Private Entry | Controlled Entry | Full Use of House\n\n2-minute walk to the bus stop, and 5 minutes to UW by bus\n\n2-minute walk to WLU, and Conestoga College\n\n5-minute walk to Walmart, plazas, and stores','2021-04-15 18:34:40','2021-04-15 18:34:40'),(10,10,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',6,700.00,'male',5,5,1,5,0,1,'ensuite','Price is negotiable and includes all utilities: hydro, internet, water, and gas\n\n- 7 min bus ride to UW\n\n- 10 min walk to WLU\n\nSuite Features:\n\n- Large rooms and windows\n\n- Private en-suite washroom (in every suite)\n\n- Fully furnished (bed, mattress, desk, chair, night table)\n\n- Furnished living rooms with large flat-screen TVs\n\n- Kitchens fully equipped with energy-saving appliances, including a full-size fridge, extra freezer, microwave, toaster oven, stovetop and dishwasher\n\nThe living room and kitchen are fully furnished as well.\n\nBuilding Features:\n\n- Laundry facilities\n\n- Furnished common room lounge with large, flat-screen TV and fireplace\n\n- Large common study area\n\n- Pool table\n\n- Available parking\n\n- Interior secure bicycle lock-up\n\n- Onsite management team and 24-hour building security\n\nLink to a virtual tour of Bridgeport House: https://www.rez-one.ca/bridgeport-house/#1580326254664-72690424-3623\n\nPlease feel free to message me for more details!','2021-04-27 23:01:39','2021-04-27 23:01:39'),(11,11,'fall,winter,spring','2021-05-13','2022-05-13',12,1750.00,'co-ed',2,5,1,1,0,0,'ensuite','Multiple units of 2 Bed + 1 Bath available:\n\n- All Fully furnished\n\n- Walking distance to UW and WLU\n\n- All utilities included (Extra for hydro)\n\n- Laundry room available\n\n- Unlimited high speed internet\n\n- Pet friendly\n\nAvailable for immediate move in!\n\nContact me for more information or questions :)','2021-05-13 14:10:05','2021-05-13 14:10:05'),(12,12,'fall','2021-09-01','2022-01-01',17,650.00,'female',1,3,0,1,0,0,'same-floor','Details:\n\n- 1 fully furnished bedroom in an apartment with 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms\n\n- ALL UTILITIES INCLUDED except hydro\n\n- located at the intersection of Columbia St & Lester St, minutes away from UW & WLU\n\n- BUS STOP RIGHT OUTSIDE\n\n- on-site laundry\n\n- nice, quiet roommates\n\n- virtual tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=jmFnrJfFADt','2021-06-21 15:08:05','2021-06-21 15:08:05'),(13,13,'winter','2021-04-26','2021-08-26',13,500.00,'female',4,4,0,2,0,0,'common','Located on Lester street, this apartment is less than 10 mins away from both Laurier and Waterloo campuses, perfect for those who have friends from both schools. This female only apartment has laundry on site, and good security to ensure safety for all tenants.','2021-04-15 12:04:08','2021-04-15 12:04:08'),(14,14,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-01','2022-09-01',11,675.00,'female',1,3,1,2,0,0,'ensuite','open, spacious apartment\n\nwith 2 balcony windows facing WLU, big living and dining area. link to virtual tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=mcY1pzDBshK','2021-05-10 21:41:26','2021-05-10 21:41:26'),(15,15,'spring','2021-05-01','2021-09-01',18,625.00,'female',1,5,1,1,1,0,'common','Clean, spacious and fully furnished, 1 bedroom apartment with a common area kitchen and living room plus an ensuite bath. Located next to Wilfrid Laurier University with shopping restaurants and shopping centers nearby within walking distance. Wifi, water, and A/C included.','2021-04-26 12:52:15','2021-04-26 12:52:15'),(16,16,'fall,winter,spring','2021-09-01','2022-09-01',9,570.00,'co-ed',1,1,0,2,0,0,'unavailable','Available: September 2021 to August 2022\n\n- Intersection of King St. and Columbia St., Waterloo, ON N2L 3K5\n\n- 1 furnished room (Room number#1) in a 5 bedroom house\n\n- All utilities included: Heat, Hydro, Water, central air condition\n\n- Free unlimited wireless internet\n\n- House includes a large fridge, microwave\n\n- 2, 3Pcs Washrooms\n\n- Furnished living and dining rooms\n\n- Professional Lawn Care and Snow Remo